Package: GSHydroTools
Type: Package
Title: Collection of functions for hydrological analysis.
Version: 1.0.2
Date: 2014-08-06
Author: Steve Corsi
Maintainer: Steve Corsi <srcorsi@usgs.gov>
Description: Collection of functions for storm volume computation (Hydrovol),
    time series data aggregation, baseflow determination, load computations,
    and spatial data visualization.
License: file LICENSE
Copyright: This software is in the public domain because it contains materials
    that originally came from the United States Geological Survey, an agency of
    the United States Department of Interior. For more information, see the
    official USGS copyright policy at
    http://www.usgs.gov/visual-id/credit_usgs.html#copyright
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
    rgdal,
    sp,
    dataRetrieval,
    USGSwsBase,
    raster,
    rgeos
Suggests:
    knitr
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
